name: BostonGlobe
text: Though Texas is traditionally a Republican stronghold, Democrats have in recent cycles hoped to flip the state’s 38 electoral votes. text: North Carolina is a major state to watch in 2020, for both the presidential race and a key Senate race that Democrats hope to win as they seek to flip the Senate. Our live results pages update every 15 seconds. https://t.co/uQkbqppzvq https://t.co/xZynYbMeVV
